OL,5, Mike Ashley is to step down from the   
OL,6, board of Frasers Group, owner of the   
OL,7, Sports Direct chain that the retail    
OL,8, billionaire founded four decades ago.  
OL,10,FMr Ashley had already handed over the  
OL,11,Frunning of the group to his son-in-law 
OL,12,FMichael Murray earlier this year.      
OL,14,FFrasers said Mr Ashley would not be    
OL,15,Fstanding for re-election as a director,
OL,16,Fand would leave the board next month.  
OL,18,FThe company also announced that Mr     
OL,19,FAshley will provide the company with   
OL,20,F#100m worth of funding.                
